{"tid":877202,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［新盤round 2] 朗城滙暫售不足3成 代理指現場不多客","createTime":"2018-10-26T07:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T14:07:48.000Z","uid":185647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8fa709ff45c3adb4a026c875b9edb1e7f00748","tid":877202,"uid":185647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/152318_92df49f5a5a56b8431e1274eff63b971.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F152318_92df49f5a5a56b8431e1274eff63b971.png&h=d54e39af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【14:49】現場消息稱，全日尾籌為368號，暫已售138伙，但現場已不多客，只餘下約20枱客在場，全日成交料140至150宗左右。<br />\n<br />\n【14:00】消息指已有逾120伙獲選購，佔是日可發售單位的逾兩成。<br />\n<br />\n西北新盤繼續登場，由華懋及港鐵合作發展的元朗朗屏站朗城滙，今日發售首批504伙，日前截收超過3000票，超額5倍。<br />\n<br />\n今日九點半大手客到場登記，售樓廠如心廣場大堂準買家陸續現身，現場出現人龍市場指共有26枱大客出席。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，早上10點半時已有15伙售出，最大為2,400萬元購入兩伙736方呎的中層3房單位。<br />\n<br />\nB組散客於早上10點開始登記，近300人於售樓廠門外排隊，人龍準買家中以年輕人為主，市場指出，散客共有250枱，現時準備抽籤揀樓。<br />\n<br />\n華懋集團銷售部總監吳崇武表示，項目現時售出20多伙，大手客中有2組客斥資約2,500萬元購入2伙三房單位，據悉用以自住。至於B組散客有360枱客出現。他相信該盤今日可以售出7至8成單位，而3房戶則相信較難一日清袋。他補充，視乎B組時段銷情最快今日加推。"},{"pid":"4151cf5576e26e5030789c4a4624c0cc3017e5f8","tid":877202,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"【14:49】現場消息稱，全日尾籌為368號，暫已售138伙，但現場已不多客，只餘下約20枱客在場，全日成交料140至150宗左右。"},{"pid":"9cc9227f53c3ed0084d0b8e7b1e14b84de6c13bb","tid":877202,"uid":40089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"開得仲貴過荃城𣿬<br />\n<br />\n傻鳩黎<br />\n<br />\n開平多5000 就有價講既"},{"pid":"06743ededaa26ce2b9e9b5d2f105b7907a4e92ca","tid":877202,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07147282b11e42ad7dbdca07ed6e5afd52a61d26","tid":877202,"uid":185647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"鐵路盤都賣唔到三成，黎緊尚悅。嶺都幾大鑊"},{"pid":"aefca3bf73564aaaa8adab1a177efef7d8153f53","tid":877202,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"又話收到3000張票? 入左票唔黎?<br />\n唔黎唔洗俾錢?"},{"pid":"1c4f556b5a7f106a3cfe6535e7af41b9f045459e","tid":877202,"uid":185647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aefca3bf73564aaaa8adab1a177efef7d8153f53","tid":877202,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"又話收到3000張票? 入左票唔黎?<br />\n唔黎唔洗俾錢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"可能d票係aa落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedb81bf530ef16bb5895e83012ddce103177901","tid":877202,"uid":41944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aefca3bf73564aaaa8adab1a177efef7d8153f53","tid":877202,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"又話收到3000張票? 入左票唔黎?<br />\n唔黎唔洗俾錢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:33:03.000Z","msg":"唔黎唔洗俾錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 入左2票，20萬係agent 公司出，我無去"},{"pid":"1ad52d49bc2f4ee43f597d73de5d61216e373164","tid":877202,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"入票數既5%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38292bc1c823531c053a10b215d02e1105aed57","tid":877202,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"盛放空前"},{"pid":"bb73fd5f4bf61f973f324b7da592b819180fa921","tid":877202,"uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"都仲有百幾個勇者算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532a4abbd7aedb6dc7efed42811d72dcc290cffd","tid":877202,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply